        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 10. Dicerapanorpa tjederi, from Yulongshan, Yunnan. (A) Male, dorsal view; (B) female, dorsal view; (C, D) genital bulb of male, dorsal and ventral views; (E) aedeagus complex, ventral view; (F) abdominal segments IX–XI of female, ventral view; (G) abdominal segments VIII–XI of female, lateral view. Scale bars: A and B = 3.0 mm; C, D, F, G = 0.5 mm; E = 0.2 mm." ;
